OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779631868
OL,3,CGreen Party MP takes leave of absence
OL,4,Cafter suffering from 'burnout'
OL,6,FCarla Denyer, the Green Party MP for
OL,7,FBristol Central, is taking a leave of
OL,8,Fabsence after suffering from burnout.
OL,10,FThe former party co-leader won her
OL,11,Fseat in the 2024 general election,
OL,12,Fbeating the former Labour MP Thangam
OL,13,FDebbonaire.
OL,15,FIn a statement released today (May
OL,16,F22), Denyer said working as an MP for
OL,17,FBristol Central had been a "privilage"
OL,18,Fbut in recent years she had struggled
OL,19,Fwith "persistant health issues".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
