PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779631868
OL,3,CGreen Party MP takes leave of absence
OL,4,Cafter suffering from 'burnout'
OL,6,FShe said "I have been trying to manage
OL,7,Fthese alongside the long hours and
OL,8,Fsignificant responsibility my work
OL,9,Fentails.
OL,11,F"It has become clear that this is not
OL,12,Fan effective strategy and that doing
OL,13,Fso is inhibiting my ability to recover.
OL,15,F"Having taken advice from my doctor, I
OL,16,Fwill be taking several weeks off in
OL,17,Forder to try to get back to full
OL,18,Fhealth."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
