PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779631868
OL,3,CGreen Party MP takes leave of absence
OL,4,Cafter suffering from 'burnout'
OL,6,FDuring her time away, the MP said that
OL,7,Fher constituency office will continue
OL,8,Fto run as usual, and encouraged
OL,9,Fconstiuents to get in touch with any
OL,10,Fissues they need help with.
OL,12,FDenyer said she wanted to be open
OL,13,Fabout suffering form "burnout" and
OL,14,Fsymptoms that arise from it.
OL,16,FShe said "Burnout is a condition that
OL,17,Fdoes not tend to get better on its
OL,18,Fown. If left unmanaged, it can worsen
OL,19,Fand increase your risk of long-term
OL,20,Fhealth problems."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779631868
OL,3,CGreen Party MP takes leave of absence
OL,4,Cafter suffering from 'burnout'
OL,6,F"This is something that I know will be
OL,7,Ffamiliar to many people in all walks
OL,8,Fof life, especially those working in
OL,9,Fhigh-stress environments and in people-
OL,10,Ffacing professions such as nurses,
OL,11,Fteachers and social workers.
OL,13,F:I hope that by sharing my own
OL,14,Fstruggles, I can help in some small
OL,15,Fway to combat the stigma around it and
OL,16,Fcontribute to a more open
OL,17,Fconversation."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
